{"tid":815859,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"法唔法國月餅文化好垃圾","createTime":"2018-09-12T10:47:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T11:07:20.000Z","uid":93036,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a0ff4b40e87765e6731b85a4d094b27cd8671042","tid":815859,"uid":93036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:47:08.000Z","msg":"好唔好食咁主觀既野我唔批評，但以下幾點都係月餅或月餅帶黎既既客觀缺點／問題<br />\n<br />\n1. 唔健康<br />\n月餅高糖高納高脂，食完又滯對健康只有壞影響，中秋食生田應節就夠<br />\n<br />\n2. 比機會炒狗搵食<br />\n好多炒狗都借炒月餅卷搵錢，壓迫港人<br />\n<br />\n3. 比機會商家打劫港人<br />\n大家如果有自己整個月餅就知成本根本好平，每盒賣兩三百profit margin極高<br />\n<br />\n4. 唔環保<br />\npacking 極多又膠兜，又包裝袋，又盒，又手抽袋全部都唔環保(雖然年登仔唔care)<br />\n<br />\n5.  制造送禮，實質係賄賂文化<br />\n好多公司會送禮比客，又或者下屬送比上司根本就係拉關係。甚至之前有個post 話好多酒樓飲茶客仔幫姿客，部長買月餅卷可以有得提早入座。送月餅根本就係鼓吹賄賂同中國人貪小便宜文化。<br />\n<br />\n我希望各位一齊可以杯葛月餅唔好買，唔好送，等月餅滯銷!!<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1706ba364a3e8eab8a2c773a302ae5dd4f8101","tid":815859,"uid":41759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:50:18.000Z","msg":"原來法國啲月餅咁唔健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買番香港月餅好啲"},{"pid":"e7862574cc0c481d453c7983c3b4b6a8d99c0bec","tid":815859,"uid":137703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:50:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e4ed4fa29c84f55d13d51dfe2eee813490b11414","tid":815859,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:54:31.000Z","msg":"吳國月餅最正"},{"pid":"feae8939c2b56d7c9393b6b3df0cebcbad1ff7a7","tid":815859,"uid":50744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:03:41.000Z","msg":"中秋 只係一盤生意"},{"pid":"dbfb64d02f81c573fa2571ac38a15430f4b47a40","tid":815859,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:06:19.000Z","msg":"紀念革命起義啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991b6c3e45b0f61017e90b18df7dcce333fae1bf","tid":815859,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T11:07:20.000Z","msg":"真係好多痴線佬"}]}